Control,'' ``Showdown'' ``Breast Men,'' ``Welcome to Sarajevo,''
``Different For Girls,'' ``Mr. Magoo,'' ``Redline,'' ``Past
Perfect,'' ``The Sender,'' ``Lewis &AMP; Clark &AMP; George,'' ``Caught
Up,'' ``Misbegotten,'' ``The Postman.''  &UR; June 30: &LR;  ``Amistad,''
``Half Baked,'' ``Retroactive,'' ``The Replacement Killers,''
``This World, Then the Fireworks,'' ``When Danger Follows You
Home,'' ``No Looking Back,'' ``When Pigs Fly,'' ``Police Story,''
``Ma Vie En Rose (My Life in Pink).''  &UR; July 1:  &LR; ``Wag the Dog.''
 &UR; July 7:  &LR; ``Good Will Hunting,'' ``The Boxer,'' ``Six O'Clock
News,'' ``Baby Monitor: Sound of Fear.''  &UR; July 14:  &LR; ``Phantoms,''
