<TEXT>
<P>
   Add N.Y. Times News Service budget for papers of Tuesday, June
16:
</P>
<P>
   &UR; CULTURE (Coded e) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   YOUNG-POETS (Taos, N.M.) _ Young poets slug it out in a verse
competition. By Bruce Weber.
</P>
<P>
   JAZZ-AWARDS (New York) _ 1st annual Jazz Awards. By Ben Ratliff.
</P>
<P>
   GUINNESS-FLEADH (New York) _ Review of the Guinness Fleadh, held
over the weekend, and which will move on to Chicago and San
Francisco later this summer. &QL; 
By Ann Powers.
</P>
