<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-15 16:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9842 &Cx1f; tab-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-X-TREME-SPORTS-GO-CHI     06-15 1269
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-X-TREME-SPORTS-GO-CHIC-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
