<HEADER>
A9879 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-X-ADVISORY-NYT &LR;      06-15 0027
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-X-ADVISORY-NYT </SLUG>
  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Subsequent filings, with appropriate codes: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   High-speed points only, with 08 and 22 optional, being foreign
points)
</P>
