<SLUG> BC-KEYRATES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
KEY RATES 
</HEADLINE>
  (lh) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the daily key rates from The New York Times.
</P>
<P>
   ---------------------Monday------Friday-------Year Ago
</P>
<P>
