<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-15 21:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0428 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ASIA-ECON-ART-375&AMP;ADD     06-15 0855
