   BC-ELDERLY-COMPUTE-NYT (moved on Sunday, June 14)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on moved on Sunday,
June 14, about computer use by elderly people misstated the
location of a retirement community that is installing high-speed
modems. It is in Laguna Hills, Calif., not Akron, Ohio.
</P>
