   BC-OBIT-ENGLISH-NYT (moved on Thursday, June 12)
</P>
<P>
   An obituary sent by the New York Times News Service on Thursday,
June 12, about Sir David English, a British newspaper editor who
was highly regarded by the royal family for his efforts to protect
the privacy of the sons of the Princess of Wales, misstated the
date of her death. It was last Aug. 31, not in September.
</P>
