<SLUG> BC-OHIO-TORNADO-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Tornado blamed for minor damage in Ohio
 &HT;    By Steve Bennish
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   DAYTON, Ohio _ A tornado caused minor damage near Greenville,
Ohio and another funnel cloud touched down briefly near Miamisburg,
Ohio during Monday's rush hour as heavy thunderstorms pounded the
area.
</P>
